I just installed SourceTree and am going through the "Welcome" screen.  I mistakenly put in the wrong username when trying to get the list of projects on stash.atlassian.com.  I got the error "Stash API call failed - lexical error: invalid char in json text." 

This looks like a recurrence of https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/SRCTREE-933 and/or https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/STASHDEV-35

I did a quick check using curl and got a json response:

{noformat}
curl https://stash.atlassian.com/rest/api/latest/projects/STASH/repos/stash/branches?start=0&limit=10

{"errors":[{"context":null,"message":"You are not permitted to access this resource","exceptionName":"com.atlassian.stash.exception.AuthorisationException"}]}
{noformat}

I don't know the rest call for "list projects".
